The paper focuses on evaluating the impact of AI-generated explanations on human performance in conducting human-AI collaborative tasks, specifically in the context of Visual Question Answering (VQA). This involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
